A character song of [[Asaka Karin]] in [[Love Live! Nijigasaki high school idol club]]. Also remains to the suit.

* A [[Blue headwear|blue]] [[tilted headwear|tiltled]] [[Mini hat|mini]] [[Top hat]] with [[hat feather]].;
* [[Jewelry]] [[earrings]];
* [[Black gloves]], [[Bridal gauntlets]], [[wrist cuffs]];
* [[Blue nails|Blue]] [[fingernails]];
* [[Single bare shoulder|Single]] [[bare shoulders|bare shoulder]];
* A Blue [[crop top]]/ [[camisole]]/ [[midriff]]/ [[blue tank top|tank top]] with [[blue bow]] and [[buttons]] on it.
* [[Blue shorts]] connect to [[blue thighhighs|dark blue]] or [[black thighhighs|black]]  [[fishnet thighhighs]] with [[garter straps]] ([[thigh strap]]).

[[Collarbone]], [[cleavage]], [[navel]] and [[mole]] [[mole on body|on body]] may be visible.
There may be [[stage lights]], [[shooting star]] in the blue background.

